  
1, 504 Absolutely Essential Words
Words are used in sentences. American and British pronunciations are provided. It is modified wherever the creator finds any inappropriate item. In addition to the original words, some synonyms and similar words are included. Please report any problem.
https://www.memrise.com/course/178434/504-absolutely-essential-words-13/

2, Word Power Made Easy
https://www.memrise.com/course/317968/word-power-made-easy-5/
高级词汇
最后要推荐的一个词书面向高阶学习者，同样在Memrise中可以找到，书名是《Word Power Made Easy》，这本书由美国著名语言学家Norman Lewis编撰，主要受众是美国高中生和大学本科生。它是一本经久不衰的畅销数十年的经典词汇书，书中的词汇是按照主题来分类的，并且通过学习这本也能让你对英文单词的词根和词源有所了解，对于进一步扩充你的词汇量大有裨益。
